#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:2
msgid "安全相关配置"
msgstr "Security-Related Configuration"

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:5
msgid "函数与类限制"
msgstr "Function and Class Restrictions"

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:6
msgid "可通过 ``disable_functions`` / ``disable_classes`` 限制PHP可调用的函数和类。"
msgstr "Use ``disable_functions`` / ``disable_classes`` to restrict the functions and classes PHP can call."

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:9
msgid "目录访问限制"
msgstr "Directory Access Restrictions"

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:10
msgid "可通过 ``open_basedir`` 限制PHP可访问的目录。"
msgstr "Use ``open_basedir`` to restrict the directories PHP can access."

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:13
msgid "远程引用限制"
msgstr "Remote Reference Restrictions"

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:14
msgid ""
"可通过 ``all_url_include`` 限制远程文件包含，默认关闭。 可通过 ``allow_url_fopen`` "
"限制打开远程文件，默认开启。"
msgstr ""
"Use ``all_url_include`` to restrict remote file inclusion; it is disabled by "
"default. Use ``allow_url_fopen`` to restrict opening remote files; it is "
"enabled by default."

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:18
msgid "Session"
msgstr "Session"

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:21
msgid "Session.Save"
msgstr "Session.Save"

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:22
msgid ""
"PHP的Session默认handler为文件，存储在 php.ini 的 ``session.save_path`` "
"中，若有任意读写文件的权限，则可修改或读取session。从phpinfo中可获得session位置。"
msgstr ""
"PHP's default Session handler is file-based and stores data under "
"``session.save_path`` in php.ini. If arbitrary file read or write access is "
"available, the session can be read or modified. The session location can be "
"obtained from phpinfo."

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:25
msgid "Session.Upload"
msgstr "Session.Upload"

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:26
msgid ""
"PHP默认开启了 ``session.upload_progress.enabled`` ， "
"该选项会导致生成上传进度文件，其存储路径可以在phpinfo中获取。"
msgstr ""
"PHP enables ``session.upload_progress.enabled`` by default. This option "
"causes upload progress files to be generated, and their storage path can be "
"obtained from phpinfo."

#: ../../source/language/php/config.rst:28
msgid "那么可以构造特别的报文向服务器发送，在有LFI的情况下即可利用。"
msgstr "A specially crafted message can then be sent to the server and exploited when LFI is present."
